`version: 1`
`title: Nimbus Gear Customer FAQs`
`url: https://nimbusgear.example/help`
`tags: [faq, support, nimbus-gear]`

How long does shipping take and what does it cost?
Standard shipping within the US and EU takes 3-5 business days and costs a flat $5.95. Express shipping (1-2 business days) is available for $14.95. All orders over $75 ship free with standard shipping — no promo code needed. Orders placed before 14:00 CET on a business day are dispatched the same day from our warehouse in Rotterdam.
`url: https://nimbusgear.example/help/shipping-times-costs`

Do you ship internationally?
Yes — Nimbus Gear ships to over 40 countries across North America, Europe, and Asia-Pacific. International delivery takes 7-14 business days and starts at $19.95, calculated at checkout based on destination and weight. Import duties and taxes for non-EU/non-US destinations are the customer's responsibility and are collected by the carrier on delivery. Battery-powered electronics may have shipping restrictions to a small number of countries; checkout will flag any affected items.
`url: https://nimbusgear.example/help/international-shipping`

What is your return policy?
You can return any item within 30 days of delivery for a full refund, as long as it is unused and in its original packaging. Defective items can be returned within the full 30-day window regardless of packaging, and we cover the return shipping for them. Refunds are issued to your original payment method within 5-7 business days after our warehouse receives and inspects the return. Final-sale items and used gift cards are not eligible for return.
`url: https://nimbusgear.example/help/return-policy`

How do I start a return or get an RMA number?
The fastest way is right here in chat — tell me you'd like to return an item and I can look up your recent order, help you pick the product, and issue an RMA number on the spot. You can also start a return from Your Account > Orders > Start a Return on our website. Every return needs an RMA number; write it on the outside of the package and include the packing slip. Once your RMA is created, we email you a prepaid return label for defective items (for other returns, a $4.95 label fee is deducted from your refund).
`url: https://nimbusgear.example/help/start-a-return`

What warranty do Nimbus Gear products have?
All Nimbus Gear products come with a 2-year limited warranty covering manufacturing defects in materials and workmanship. The warranty starts on the delivery date and requires proof of purchase (your order number is enough). It does not cover normal wear and tear, accidental damage, or water damage beyond a product's stated rating. Warranty claims are handled through the same RMA process as returns — contact support or start a claim in chat.
`url: https://nimbusgear.example/help/warranty`

What payment methods do you accept?
We accept Visa, Mastercard, American Express, PayPal, Apple Pay, Google Pay, and Klarna (pay in 3 interest-free installments). Nimbus Gear gift cards can be combined with any other payment method. Your card is only charged when your order ships, not when you place it. We do not accept cash on delivery or bank transfers.
`url: https://nimbusgear.example/help/payment-methods`

Can I change or cancel my order after placing it?
You can change or cancel an order free of charge within 1 hour of placing it, from Your Account > Orders or by asking here in chat. After that, our warehouse starts picking and we can no longer guarantee changes. If your order has already shipped, simply refuse the delivery or use our standard 30-day return process once it arrives. Address changes are possible until the order status shows "Shipped".
`url: https://nimbusgear.example/help/order-changes`

How do I reset my account password?
Go to the login page and click "Forgot password?" — we'll email you a secure reset link that is valid for 60 minutes. If the email doesn't arrive within a few minutes, check your spam folder and confirm you used the address on your account. For security reasons, support agents can never see or set your password. If you no longer have access to your email address, contact support to verify your identity and update it.
`url: https://nimbusgear.example/help/password-reset`

How do I track my order?
As soon as your order ships you'll receive an email with the carrier name and tracking number, and tracking is also shown under Your Account > Orders. You can also ask me here in chat — just share your order number (it looks like NG-1042) and I'll check the current status for you. Tracking events can take up to 24 hours to appear after dispatch. We ship with DHL, UPS, and PostNL depending on your region.
`url: https://nimbusgear.example/help/order-tracking`

Do you sell gift cards?
Yes — digital gift cards are available in amounts from $25 to $500 and are delivered by email within minutes of purchase. Gift cards never expire and can be spent across multiple orders; any unused balance stays on the card. They can be combined with promo codes and other payment methods at checkout. Gift cards cannot be refunded or exchanged for cash once redeemed.
`url: https://nimbusgear.example/help/gift-cards`

How do I use a promo code?
Enter your promo code in the "Promo code" field at checkout and click Apply before paying — the discount shows immediately in your order summary. Only one promo code can be used per order, and codes cannot be applied retroactively after an order is placed. Some codes exclude sale items or gift cards; the terms are listed with each promotion. If a valid code isn't working, ask me in chat and I can check it for you.
`url: https://nimbusgear.example/help/promo-codes`

How do I find the right size or fit?
Every apparel and footwear product page has a size guide link with measurements in both cm and inches. Nimbus Gear apparel generally runs true to size; if you're between sizes for insulated jackets, we recommend sizing up to allow for layering. For backpacks, check the torso-length range listed in the specifications. And remember — if the fit isn't right, exchanges within 30 days are free.
`url: https://nimbusgear.example/help/sizing-fit`

What is Nimbus Gear doing about sustainability?
Our packaging is 100% plastic-free and made from recycled cardboard, and we offset the carbon footprint of every shipment. Over 60% of our apparel line uses recycled or bluesign-certified fabrics, with a goal of 90% by 2028. Through our Nimbus Renewed program you can trade in used Nimbus Gear equipment for store credit, and we refurbish and resell it. Repair guides and spare parts for our electronics are available free on our website.
`url: https://nimbusgear.example/help/sustainability`

How can I contact customer support and what are your hours?
Our support team is available Monday to Friday, 9:00-18:00 CET. You can reach us via this chat (the fastest option — I'm here 24/7), by email at support@nimbusgear.example, or by phone at +31 20 555 0142 during business hours. Email replies typically arrive within one business day. Outside business hours I can still help with order tracking, returns, and most other questions right here in chat.
`url: https://nimbusgear.example/help/contact-support`
